config BR2_PACKAGE_THINGINO_PRUSA_CONNECT
	bool "Thingino Prusa Connect integration"
	help
	  Upload Thingino camera metadata and snapshots directly to the
	  Prusa Connect cloud service. Includes:
	  - init script and daemon that periodically push /tmp/snapshot.jpg
	    and device information to the Prusa Connect API
	  - CLI helper for configuring tokens/fingerprints from SSH
	  - WebUI page (needs thingino-webui) for credential entry

